{"tid":1024680,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［人生交叉點］返工中刺針，去醫院？返工？","createTime":"2019-02-16T18:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T22:31:06.000Z","uid":157396,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d775e36bce592c789e1200c082f5d110cae8c9cd","tid":1024680,"uid":157396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"比呢個post啟發到<br />\n<br />\n巴士刺客再現港島　女乘客遭刺針拮中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1022489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1022489</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果個日你趕返工係開個好重要既會，成10幾人，大老世，你個部門主管，總之d大粒野係哂到，個powerpoint係你到，present又係你主力講，但你返工既時候中左針，唔影響你活動能力，但你明知去醫院驗完傷冇乜事架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後你地會選擇返工定去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係我，我可能都係會揀返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然如果唔係咁重要就梗係去醫院請SL啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd0b7fd472b0156b98d348b75ee64b75895b283","tid":1024680,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T18:21:36.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"fc5b8413db36a0dd5d2f7f2ba3c4d2c3ed8ee00b","tid":1024680,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T22:31:06.000Z","msg":"如果唔present會俾人炒的話，<br />\n咪present完先，<br />\nNeedle stick injury 一個鐘後睇醫生，<br />\n同幾個鐘頭後睇醫生，分別唔大。"}]}